{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","text":"WCAG21Requirements","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/WCAG21Requirements"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"title":"requirementsAA","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV14requirementsAASb7textual_Sb10nonTextualtvp","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"WCAG21Requirements","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/requirementsAA"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"WCAG 2.1 requirement for AA level needs to have textual component matching 4.5:1 contrast ratio"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and non textual component matching 3:1 contrast ratio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is recommended for web projects."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/requirementsaa"]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is for example the case for France with the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"also named “RGAA”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron).","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","type":"topic"},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","type":"link","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.nu